[
    {
        "text": "So, you may have heard about Ponzi schemes in the news.",
        "startTime": 318,
        "endTime": 3573,
        "slowStartTime": 627,
        "slowEndTime": 5585
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody knows they're illegal, but you might not understand how they work.",
        "startTime": 3959,
        "endTime": 7477,
        "slowStartTime": 6088,
        "slowEndTime": 11440
    },
    {
        "text": "So, Ben is here to show us.",
        "startTime": 7863,
        "endTime": 9255,
        "slowStartTime": 11945,
        "slowEndTime": 14108
    },
    {
        "text": "To start off, Ben gets a few people to invest their money with him.",
        "startTime": 9516,
        "endTime": 13128,
        "slowStartTime": 14424,
        "slowEndTime": 19917
    },
    {
        "text": "At the end of the year, he gives those clients amazing returns...",
        "startTime": 13469,
        "endTime": 17101,
        "slowStartTime": 20354,
        "slowEndTime": 25876
    },
    {
        "text": "...that beats every other investor in the market.",
        "startTime": 17197,
        "endTime": 19199,
        "slowStartTime": 25945,
        "slowEndTime": 29023
    },
    {
        "text": "Needless to say, the investors are thrilled.",
        "startTime": 19692,
        "endTime": 22061,
        "slowStartTime": 29688,
        "slowEndTime": 33316
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, they're so ecstatic about all the money they're making...",
        "startTime": 23069,
        "endTime": 26533,
        "slowStartTime": 34754,
        "slowEndTime": 40024
    },
    {
        "text": "...that they tell all their friends and family about it too.",
        "startTime": 27047,
        "endTime": 29510,
        "slowStartTime": 40721,
        "slowEndTime": 44490
    },
    {
        "text": "Who tell their friends, who tell their friends.",
        "startTime": 29878,
        "endTime": 32524,
        "slowStartTime": 44967,
        "slowEndTime": 49011
    },
    {
        "text": "In the stock market, most investors make money some years and lose money others.",
        "startTime": 33096,
        "endTime": 38103,
        "slowStartTime": 49794,
        "slowEndTime": 57379
    },
    {
        "text": "But Ben's Ponzi scheme?",
        "startTime": 38445,
        "endTime": 39753,
        "slowStartTime": 57818,
        "slowEndTime": 59855
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, it never loses money.",
        "startTime": 40251,
        "endTime": 42085,
        "slowStartTime": 60527,
        "slowEndTime": 63353
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, it always beats the market by a huge margin.",
        "startTime": 42480,
        "endTime": 45575,
        "slowStartTime": 63870,
        "slowEndTime": 68587
    },
    {
        "text": "But the returns he pays to these people aren't from actual profits.",
        "startTime": 46011,
        "endTime": 50375,
        "slowStartTime": 69167,
        "slowEndTime": 75788
    },
    {
        "text": "He just takes the money these new guys invest and gives it to these guys.",
        "startTime": 50711,
        "endTime": 54825,
        "slowStartTime": 76217,
        "slowEndTime": 82462
    },
    {
        "text": "But as soon as you can't get enough new money from this group to pay these people,...",
        "startTime": 55249,
        "endTime": 59755,
        "slowStartTime": 83024,
        "slowEndTime": 89858
    },
    {
        "text": "...then the whole pyramid starts to crumble because they're not getting paid anymore.",
        "startTime": 60148,
        "endTime": 63868,
        "slowStartTime": 90372,
        "slowEndTime": 96027
    },
    {
        "text": "Ben and these guys who invested first made a killing...",
        "startTime": 64343,
        "endTime": 67602,
        "slowStartTime": 96665,
        "slowEndTime": 101628
    },
    {
        "text": "...but these folks lost all their money.",
        "startTime": 67903,
        "endTime": 69701,
        "slowStartTime": 102005,
        "slowEndTime": 104777
    },
    {
        "text": "So the next time a guy like Ben...",
        "startTime": 70595,
        "endTime": 72219,
        "slowStartTime": 106042,
        "slowEndTime": 108554
    },
    {
        "text": "...tries to get you to invest in something that sounds too good to be true,...",
        "startTime": 72297,
        "endTime": 75407,
        "slowStartTime": 108596,
        "slowEndTime": 113336
    },
    {
        "text": "...it probably is.",
        "startTime": 75779,
        "endTime": 76863,
        "slowStartTime": 113818,
        "slowEndTime": 115519
    },
    {
        "text": "Just ask Ben.",
        "startTime": 77439,
        "endTime": 78305,
        "slowStartTime": 116308,
        "slowEndTime": 117683
    }
]